4,"uid":120205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T07:22:04.000Z","msg":"留名學嘢 大師快啲請教下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e656f1c332707f2c785c3d8bd4aee4e50d760b9e","tid":276624,"uid":55296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T09:10:10.000Z","msg":"老實講你教返我轉頭啦"},{"pid":"a3112f1288439cfbaa323f4b8fb2665806f7583a","tid":276624,"uid":111417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T13:26:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老實講你教返我轉頭啦</blockquote><br />\n其實我策略都係高賣低買。一年前見個股市在相對低位咪轉晒香港股票基金囉，到覺得股市差唔多到頂回落又轉晒均衡，賺波幅。都係純粹個人感覺。"},{"pid":"d5fc213003c1ab56a4efa8061fe8e9c17ca6e67f","tid":276624,"uid":108146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T13:28:08.000Z","msg":"轉組合駛唔駛手續費架？"},{"pid":"e7961e485d5731e395a67538ca4d4cfb70c7915f","tid":276624,"uid":61770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T13:58:27.000Z","msg":"有自願供款？ 月入起碼三萬樓上"},{"pid":"e6802f64440648c702ce5049b1c814e6737d4caf","tid":276624,"uid":82394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T16:44:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a867b289ab5b64d3d663e120a5aa3597c21638c","tid":276624,"uid":111417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T06:59:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>轉組合駛唔駛手續費架？</blockquote><br />\n唔使呀，而家大部份公司都係無限轉架啦"},{"pid":"0ad07835c3b7592be259af80d371821c15c6d7d4","tid":276624,"uid":111417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T07:00:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有自願供款？ 月入起碼三萬樓上</blockquote><br />\n無呀，公司額外幫我供小小"},{"pid":"9078a6b7d2abb3074e6b2c3292feb77a0acf19c8","tid":276624,"uid":111417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T02:39:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/vewxqcku\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvewxqcku&h=48b4c1d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想保持返呢個賺幅應該點改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nHello 大家好, 又係我!<br />\n兩個月又過去了, 同大家分享下強積金投資之道。<br />\npo完上次張圖之後, 我將強積金投資策略由100%香港股票基金轉左做60%香港股票基金同40%平穩基金, 先鎖定40%香港股票基金之利潤, 食左糊先。<br />\n下圖係今日既收益, 因為2個月前覺得股市高高地所以先行獲利, 否則今日結餘可能仲多, 不過唔緊要, 因為無人可以賺到牛市的最後一刻, 而且仲有60%組合跟港股同步。<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/p0al98eh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fp0al98eh&h=d4f9b0be&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f92e78bcf5c274635ba6a7699518e5d77e66a4ea","tid":276624,"uid":36297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T07:17:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/vewxqcku\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvewxqcku&h=48b4c1d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想保持返呢個賺幅應該點改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nHello 大家好, 又係我!<br />\n兩個月又過去了, 同大家分享下強積金投資之道。<br />\npo完上次張圖之後, 我將強積金投資策略由100%香港股票基金轉左做60%香港股票基金同40%平穩基金, 先鎖定40%香港股票基金之利潤, 食左糊先。<br />\n下圖係今日既收益, 因為2個月前覺得股市高高地所以先行獲利, 否則今日結餘可能仲多, 不過唔緊要, 因為無人可以賺到牛市的最後一刻, 而且仲有60%組合跟港股同步。<br />\n[mg]<a href=\"https://holland.pk/p0al98eh[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fp0al98eh%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=Qt0MqXQlWJQZma1h94VKXZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=2ee9c16f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://holland.pk/p0al98eh[/img]</a></blockquote><br />\n想學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}